languages.text: "Чего умолк? Продолжай восхвалять меня! Если мне понравится — пощажу".
"Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."
languages.original_text: "Чего умолк? Продолжай восхвалять меня! Если мне понравится — пощажу".

languages.text: “怎么突然安静了？继续赞美我呀，来啊！如果夸得我开心，我就饶了你们。”
languages.original_text: "Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."

traits.locale_text: “怎么突然安静了？继续赞美我呀，来啊！如果夸得我开心，我就饶了你们。”

languages.text: "Warum das Schweigen? Nur zu, lobt mich weiter! Wenn es mir gefällt, verschone ich Euch."
languages.original_text: "Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."

traits.locale_text: "Warum das Schweigen? Nur zu, lobt mich weiter! Wenn es mir gefällt, verschone ich Euch."

languages.text: «¿A qué viene ese silencio? ¡Vamos, sigue alabándome! Si me complaces, igual os perdono la vida».
languages.original_text: "Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."

traits.locale_text: «¿A qué viene ese silencio? ¡Vamos, sigue alabándome! Si me complaces, igual os perdono la vida».

languages.text: « Pourquoi ce silence ? Continuez, louez ma venue ! Si vous réussissez à me satisfaire, je vous épargnerai. »
languages.original_text: "Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."

traits.locale_text: « Pourquoi ce silence ? Continuez, louez ma venue ! Si vous réussissez à me satisfaire, je vous épargnerai. »

languages.text: 「なぜ黙っている？さあ、私を讃えよ！気に入れば、命は助けてやる」
languages.original_text: "Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."

traits.locale_text: 「なぜ黙っている？さあ、私を讃えよ！気に入れば、命は助けてやる」

languages.text: "Bu sükûn da neyin nesi? Devam et, övgü yağdırmaya devam et! Övgülerinden hoşnut kalırsam canını bağışlayacağım."
languages.original_text: "Why the silence? Go on, keep praising me! If I like it, I shall spare you."
